00:17:08,320 --> 00:17:09,651
Tối nay rất vui.

227
00:17:11,040 --> 00:17:12,246
Giỏi lắm, anh bạn.

228
00:17:42,840 --> 00:17:43,880
<i>Chúng ta an toàn ở đây.</i>

229
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,295
<i>WICKED là tốt.</i>

230
00:17:45,320 --> 00:17:46,415
<i>Ngoài đó có gì?</i>

231
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:48,124
